descriptionHtml: Overwolf is a free Overlay mod full of many different utilities you can use while playing Skyrim. Its features include video and screen capture, an in-game browser, multi-chat functionality and much more! We will soon add the mod seen on this video: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5SmBZ9IH2hE to allow players to play Skyrim on Windows 8 touch enabled machines! (AKA Skyrim on a tablet!)
author: Overwolf
